"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1045922","Ministry of Defence","false","2019-01-28","<p>Two Royal Navy Mine Countermeasures Vessels (MCMVs) will participate in this activity. MCMVs typically have a crew of between 35 to 50 personnel.</p>","Milton Keynes North","Mark Lancaster","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1045922/answer",,,,,,"2019-01-28T14:57:34.073Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1045922/answer","Biography information for Mark Lancaster","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1045922/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2019-01-22","Saudi Arabia: Joint Exercises","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, pursuant to the Answer of 13 December 2018 to Question 200616 on Saudi Arabia: Joint Exercises, (a) how many personnel and (b) what Royal Navy assets will take part in the Royal Navy Passage Exercise with Saudi Arabia between 3 and 7 February 2019.","false","Biography information for Nia Griffith","Llanelli","Nia Griffith","211136"
